title: Hour 3 - PGA Responds to LIV Golf
itunes:title: Hour 3 - PGA Responds to LIV Golf
description:
Dan Patrick reacts to the news that Tiger Woods and Rory McIlroy will spearhead a new golf league in partnership with the PGA Tour. The guys talk Russell Westbrook, Andrew Luck, Brian Kelly, and much more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
